Here is a beta version of my map. The counterterrorist are invisible and have a knife. Terrorists can spawner objects and other may have a weapon_laser or shield ...
The map has texture cs_office. There are a lot of easter eggs and buttons.
There are libraries and frameworks that open, doors trapped, a tank of gas that can explode a room where the monitor change frame every 5 seconds ... many possibilities. This is a map of average size.
